metadata.name: Couch Guyz #1
metadata.description: Couch Guyz is a collection of 3328 Guyz and 5 extremely rare Couch Girlz. From the artist of Llamaverse, SpitBuddies and Llamascape and the founder of Luminal Genesis/Universe. The Developers of Luminal Genesis, Wunks, Snuggle Buddies Genesis and NeoToyko Punks. The Couch Guyz hub will be a worry-free safe haven for all the latest news, updates, giveaways and community raffles within the NFT space.
